          { "question": "Interview: Your CEO wants a daily sales dashboard. What's your BI workflow from start to finish?", "options": ["Build charts first, then connect data", "Connect to data source, transform data, model relationships, design visuals, publish and share", "Write a Python script and email the output", "Ask someone else to do it"], "correctAnswerIndex": 1 },
