        "content": "Build your first BI report:\n\n1. **Create sample data** — a small sales table (date, product, region, amount)\n2. **Load into Power BI/Tableau** (or use any free tool like Google Looker Studio)\n3. **Add a calculated column** for profit (amount * 0.7 as assumed margin)\n4. **Create a bar chart** showing sales by product\n5. **Create a line chart** showing sales over time\n6. **Add a slicer/filter** for region\n\nArrange into a simple one-page report. Export as PDF or image.\n\n:::checkpoint\nWhat's the minimum needed for a useful BI report?\nA) 10 charts and lots of colors\nB) Connected data, a meaningful chart, and a filter\nC) Real-time data connection\nD) A published dashboard online\nCorrect: B",
