        "content": "Get application-ready:\n\n1. **Tailor your resume** for a specific target role (find a real job posting)\n2. **Update bullet points** using action verbs and measurable impact\n3. **Optimize your LinkedIn** — headline, about, featured, experience\n4. **Send 5 connection requests** to people in your target industry\n5. **Create an application tracker** — spreadsheet with role, company, date applied, status, follow-up\n\nApplying without tracking is like running an analysis without documenting your steps. A tracker keeps you organized.\n\n:::checkpoint\nWhat should you track in a job application tracker?\nA) Only the company name\nB) Role, company, date applied, status, and follow-up notes\nC) Just the salary\nD) Nothing — track in your head\nCorrect: B",
